  86:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma_ex.c ****               The DMA channel transfers can be conditioned by hardware signals edges (rising or fal
  87:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma_ex.c ****               triggers. Trigger condition can be applied at :
  88:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma_ex.c ****                (++) Single/Burst level :
  89:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma_ex.c ****                     Each single/burst data transmission is conditioned by a signal trigger hit.
